long sleever
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A long beer-glass, or glass of beer, cf long beer.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka long-sleever, sleever (see); ca1950 Havelock, for a large (? 12oz) glass. -->19- Partridge D.S. P.- ca1888 (Morris): obsolesc.
